          "reviewBody": "If there was any rating less than 1 i will give to this school. they have no regards for kids and parents. They are very soft and nice at the beginning and as soon you pay the fees they show the reality. They dont care about any physical or mental wellbeing of child. The principal is the most manipulate,cruel, heartless person in this world. Please invest your hard earned money elsewhere. This school is a waste of money,time and mental strength. They will only curb your child's potential and break their spirit,and I will never understand why. Please Do NOT enroll your child in this school. There are much better options.",
